(46089, 'C3DDC96C-0766-456F-B5D7-F2E467887ABF', 'It’s also important to note that I️ did not ask you to not be monogamous in April. I am not asking you to shut down non monogamy. I️ asked you to create distance from Ilsa because you hadn’t done it when you said you were doing it. If you want to go out on a date with anyone else, you are welcome to. Just want to be sure I️’m clear. I️’m not choosing who you date. Ilsa is in the cards for forever as far as I️’m concerned. I️ was just asking you to create distance for one month since you didn’t follow through on our agreement. We never built in a clause for what happens if one of us violates agreements, we just said that if one person feels unsafe they can turn it off for everyone. I️ don’t feel unsafe. I️ feel my trust has been violated. And I️ wish there was some kind of agreement that we could add in for that. Because it’s a different circumstance. the byproduct of that violation is that I️ just cannot be close to you when I️ know you are going to see her so soon after you violated our agreement. That is why I️ am asking you to do me the favor of having a month of distance. If seeing Ilsa matters more to you than our connection, I️ understand that parody matters to you above everything else. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-03-24T23:50:14.532907'),
