(46101, '1901259F-14F7-42CF-B5D8-D3BC851B1A92', 'Love, I want to share with you some thoughts I wrote down on Wednesday but wanted time to process on my own and with Priscilla’s guidance. I will come to this conversation with an open heart and mind. We both have a lot of active pain to work through…..  Love, I’m really struggling today about you and joe and how we’ve left things. It’s just activated so much anger and hurt. It’s very hard for me to accept stretching to work with you going out with joe at a conference while on the same night  making a sacrifice to rebuild trust with you in my communication with Ilsa.  I’m not okay with you being with Joe…I have no track record of trust with you when it comes to this relationship….Do I trust you….yes…I do…we’ve worked hard and continue to work hard at this…but this relationship to me is so radioactive that I am shaking right now just thinking about it.  and I get that I really don’t have a choice….that in our non monogamy we don’t get to chose. If that is true, then why do you get to chose who I go out with the night you are out with Joe?   I acknowledge and am accountable for not getting my communication cadence right. And that I have work to do to figure out what’s beneath this pattern. And I am motivated and committed to doing this work….to get better. I can’t promise perfection here. I wasn’t even conscious that I was off track.     And, I need acknowledgment of the extraordinary stretch I am making for you, despite the hurt,  and that there is not a double standard at play in choosing who we get to see and when we get to see which partners.   It just keeps resurfacing for me…and I’m really struggling with it…', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-03-25T08:39:22.105449'),
